#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:1
msgid "API Design"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:3
msgid ""
"RONL Business API follows the **Dutch Government API Design Rules** "
"(Nederlandse API Strategie). The API is versioned, uses standard HTTP "
"semantics, and provides machine-readable metadata via response headers."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:7
msgid "Versioning"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:9
msgid ""
"All current endpoints are served under the `/v1/` prefix (rule API-20: major "
"version in the URI path). A response header `API-Version` is added to every "
"response (rule API-57):"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:11
msgid ""
"HTTP/1.1 200 OK\n"
"API-Version: 1.0.0\n"
"Content-Type: application/json"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:17
msgid ""
"Legacy endpoints under `/api/*` continue to work but are deprecated. They "
"return additional headers (rule API-51):"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:19
msgid ""
"Deprecation: true\n"
"Link: </v1/health>; rel=\"successor-version\""
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:24
msgid "Legacy support will be removed in v2.0.0."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:28
msgid "Naming conventions"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:30
msgid "Rule"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:30
msgid "Applied as"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:30
msgid "API-05: use nouns"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:30
msgid "`process`, `decision`, `health`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:30
msgid "API-54: plural/singular"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:30
msgid ""
"Collections use plural (`/v1/process`), single resource uses singular with ID"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:30
msgid "API-48: no trailing slashes"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:30
msgid "Enforced in routing configuration"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:30
msgid "API-53: hide implementation"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:30
msgid "No Operaton-internal identifiers exposed in responses"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:30
msgid "API-04: language"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:30
msgid ""
"Technical endpoints in English; business variable names follow Dutch source "
"data"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:40
msgid "Request / response format"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:42
msgid ""
"All endpoints use `application/json`. Request bodies are validated using "
"`express-validator`. Responses follow a consistent envelope:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:44
msgid "**Success:**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:45
msgid ""
"{\n"
"  \"success\": true,\n"
"  \"data\": { ... },\n"
"  \"timestamp\": \"2026-02-20T10:00:00.000Z\"\n"
"}"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:53
msgid "**Error:**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:54
msgid ""
"{\n"
"  \"success\": false,\n"
"  \"error\": {\n"
"    \"code\": \"VALIDATION_ERROR\",\n"
"    \"message\": \"income must be a positive number\"\n"
"  },\n"
"  \"timestamp\": \"2026-02-20T10:00:00.000Z\"\n"
"}"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:67
msgid "Rate limiting headers"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:69
msgid ""
"Rate limit state is communicated via standard headers (`RateLimit-Limit`, "
"`RateLimit-Remaining`, `RateLimit-Reset`) when approaching the limit."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:73
msgid "OpenAPI documentation"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:75
msgid ""
"An OpenAPI 3.0 specification is planned at `/v1/openapi.json` (rule API-16 / "
"API-51). It is currently enabled only in non-production environments via "
"`ENABLE_SWAGGER=true`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:79
msgid "Route inventory"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cfeatures%5Capi-design.md:81
msgid ""
"The full list of registered routes, including legacy `/api/*` equivalents, "
"is documented in [API Endpoints]{1}."
msgstr ""
